### 0008_backfill_client_record_ids_wave1
- Data migration only.
- Backfills `annual_reports.client_record_id`, `vat_work_items.client_record_id`,
  `tax_deadlines.client_record_id`, `binders.client_record_id`, and
  `advance_payments.client_record_id` from legacy `client_id`.
- Backfills `businesses.legal_entity_id` from legacy `client_id`.
- Mapping assumption: `client_records.id == clients.id` for existing seed data.

### 0007_add_client_record_id_to_advance_payments
- Additive only. Adds `advance_payments.client_record_id` (nullable FK → `client_records.id`).

### 0006_add_client_record_id_to_binders
